name: stupefying time-slaughter
description:
november 15th 2021

time has stupored to a 
slow since Sunday.
mornings are manageable,
i can figure out enough to do,
but after two naps,
pack of cigs, and
sacrificing my firstborn 
child for fun, it seems 
i am running out of things 
to do.
it’s 3:52 and i don’t 
know what to do.

---
